N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 303.9 - Aed replacement schedule

State Regulations

After the initial installation, a replacement schedule
which considers the useful life of the AED units shall be developed by the

State agency. The replacement schedule should be updated
periodically. Notes
